Hi,
I do it like this:
-> Reconfigure port switch to use B server
-> Backup A server
-> Replay B server journals on A server
-> Switch to A server
-> Backup B server
-> Replay A server journals on B server
-> Reconfigure port switch to dynamic mode
							Regards,
							Thunder
